          "text": "In 2017, Gaia Trust helped to organize a meeting in Denmark between different organizations involved in local and bioregional cooperative development including AndelsTanken, the PROUT Institute, Transition USA, Gaia Education, the Samsoe Energy Academy and others (see report of the meeting). The video below is an excellent presentation by Jason Schreiner of the PROUT Institute on the subject of building localized and regionalized economies and the role of cooperatives in taking that path. It mentions another fascinating example of a very successful cooperative network in India: the Timbaktu Collective.",
